Text:
This may be a fake !
No viruses were detected however the installer had some corrupted graphics and it wanted to install a bunch of toolbars, put icons for them on the desktop as well as change my default search provider to something called "Whitesmoke".

The option to install without the garbage was grayed out.

Just thought I should warn some people who might be wary of such things.

BTW the screenshot above is from NFS3 not NFS:HP (2010)
